[25.009423, "o", "tting? Read the project\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K  config and tell me the current values. Do not print any secrets, API keys, or tokens.\u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(31576 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(7.0s)\u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mSHOW intent — pure read, no write. User wants project-scope :default-agent and :max-iterations. I'll \u001b[0m\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mread the :agent section at :project scope. No secrets involved in these keys.\u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mconfig$read\u001b[0m({\"section\" :agent, \"scope\" :project}): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 2ms, 5.2k chars\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;96m+\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 2 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(10.3s)\u001b[0m\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2m## Project Config — `:agent` Section **Source:** `.brainyard/config.edn` (project scope) | Setting | \u001b[0m\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mProject value | Notes | |---|---|---| | `:default-agent` | *(not set at project scope)* | No \u001b[0m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mproject-level override — falls back to"]
[25.009889, "o", " the system default | | `:max-iterations` | **100** | \u001b[0m\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mEffective runtime value | - The project config.edn has **no persisted `:agent` section** (`{:agent \u001b[0m\u001b[25;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mnil}`) — so there are no project-specific overrides for these keys. - `:max-iterations` resolves to \u001b[0m\u001b[26;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2m**100** (effective runtime). - `:default-agent` is **not explicitly set** in this project; it uses \u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mthe inherited default. - No secrets were read or surfaced. > Want me to pin either value at project \u001b[0m\u001b[28;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mscope? I can propose a diff and apply it on your confirmation.\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;93m⠏\u001b[0m\u001b[2m]\u001b[0m \u001b[96mConsidering...\u001b[0m\u001b[2m (17.1s)\u001b[0m\u001b[30;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────"]
