[39.025125, "o", "t\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K  config and tell me the current values. Do not print any secrets, API keys, or tokens.\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(31576 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(7.0s)\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mSHOW intent — pure read, no write. User wants project-scope :default-agent and :max-iterations. I'll \u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mread the :agent section at :project scope. No secrets involved in these keys.\u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mconfig$read\u001b[0m({\"section\" :agent, \"scope\" :project}): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 2ms, 5.2k chars\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;96m+\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 2 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(24.3s)\u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2m## Project Config — `:agent` settings Read from project config at: \u001b[0m\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2m`…/by-tut-12-configuring-brainyard-…/.brainyard/config.edn` | Setting | Value | Source | \u001b[0m\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2m|---|---|---| | `:default-agent` | *not set in project config* | falls back to runtime/built-in "]
[39.025151, "o", "\u001b[0m\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mdefault | | `:max-iterations` | **100** | effective runtime value | ### Notes - The project \u001b[0m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2m`config.edn` has **no persisted `:agent` section** (`:persisted {:agent nil}`) — neither \u001b[0m\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2m`:default-agent` nor `:max-iterations` is explicitly written at project scope. - `:max-iterations` \u001b[0m\u001b[25;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mresolves to **100** via the runtime/schema default. - `:default-agent` has no project-scope \u001b[0m\u001b[26;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2moverride; the runtime uses its built-in default. - No secrets are present in these keys. To pin \u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2meither value for this repo, I can write `[:agent :default-agent]` and/or `[:agent :max-iterations]` \u001b[0m\u001b[28;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mto the **project** config — just say the word and I'll preview the diff before applying.\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;93m⠏\u001b[0m\u001b[2m]\u001b[0m \u001b[96mDeliberating...\u001b[0m\u001b[2m (31.2s)\u001b[0m"]
