[79.207974, "o", "t\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K  config and tell me the current values. Do not print any secrets, API keys, or tokens.\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(31576 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(7.0s)\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mSHOW intent — pure read, no write. User wants project-scope :default-agent and :max-iterations. I'll \u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mread the :agent section at :project scope. No secrets involved in these keys.\u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mconfig$read\u001b[0m({\"section\" :agent, \"scope\" :project}): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 2ms, 5.2k chars\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 2 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(39.4s)\u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;96m+\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 3 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(25.1s)\u001b[0m\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2m## Project Config — `:default-agent` & `:max-iterations` **Scope:** project \u001b[0m\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2m(`<repo>/.brainyard/config.edn`) | Setting | Persisted (project) | Effective (runtime) | \u001b[0m\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2m|---"]
[79.208012, "o", "|---|---| | `:default-agent` | *not set* (`:agent` section is `nil`) | falls back to system \u001b[0m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mdefault | | `:max-iterations` | *not set* | **100** | - The project's `config.edn` has **no `:agent` \u001b[0m\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2moverrides** persisted (`:persisted {:agent nil}`). - The **effective `:max-iterations` is `100`** \u001b[0m\u001b[25;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2m(schema/runtime default, since the project file doesn't override it). - **`:default-agent` is not \u001b[0m\u001b[26;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mexplicitly configured** at project scope — the runtime uses the built-in default agent. - No secrets \u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mread or displayed. > Tip: to pin these for the repo, I can write `[:agent :default-agent]` and \u001b[0m\u001b[28;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2m`[:agent :max-iterations]` to project scope — just say the values.\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;93m⠴\u001b[0m\u001b[2m]\u001b[0m \u001b[96mDeliberating...\u001b[0m\u001b[2m (1m 11s)\u001b[0m"]
