[94.279704, "o", "\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mProject Config — Agent Settings\u001b[0m                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m Read from project scope: \u001b[36m<repo>/.brainyard/config.edn\u001b[0m                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mSetting\u001b[0m       \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mPersisted (project)\u001b[0m              \u001b[2m "]
[94.279715, "o", "│ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mEffective (runtime)\u001b[0m                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m───────────────┼───────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────\u001b[0m                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mdefault-agent\u001b[0m \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m_not set_ (\u001b[36m:agent\u001b[0m section is \u001b[36mnil\u001b[0m)\u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mfalls back to built-in default                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mmax-iterations\u001b[0m\u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m_not set_                        \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97m100\u001b[0m                                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mNotes\u001b[0m                                                                                            "]
[94.279786, "o", "      \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • The project's \u001b[36mconfig.edn\u001b[0m has \u001b[1;97mno explicit \u001b[36m:agent\u001b[0m section\u001b[0m — both keys are unset at project scope, so \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m     they inherit runtime/schema defaults.                                                              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[36m:max-iterations\u001b[0m resolves to \u001b[1;97m100\u001b[0m at runtime.                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[36m:default-agent\u001b[0m has no persisted project value; the runtime uses its built-in default.              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • No secrets, API keys, or tokens were read or shown.                                                \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[32m│ \u001b[0mIf you want to pin either value for this repo, I can write \u001b[36m[:agent :defa"]
[94.279805, "o", "ult-agent]\u001b[0m and/or \u001b[36m[:agent\u001b[0m    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[32m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[36m:max-iterations]\u001b[0m to project scope — just say the word and I'll preview the diff first.               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\r\n\u001b[92m└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\u001b[0m"]
