[98.125789, "o", "\u001b[1;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 3 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(34879 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(40.0s)\u001b[0m\u001b[2;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mSHOW intent — pure read. I already read the :agent section at :project scope in iteration 1. The \u001b[0m\u001b[3;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mpersisted project config shows {:agent nil} — no explicit :agent section is set in the project's \u001b[0m\u001b[4;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mconfig.edn. The runtime effective value for :max-iterations is 100. :default-agent is not persisted \u001b[0m\u001b[5;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mat project scope (nil). No secrets involved. I have enough to answer without re-reading.\u001b[0m\u001b[6;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[7;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\u001b[0m\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mProject Config — Agent Settings\u001b[0m "]
[98.125831, "o", "                                                                       \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m Read from project scope: \u001b[36m<repo>/.brainyard/config.edn\u001b[0m                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[12;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mSetting\u001b[0m       \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mPersisted (project)\u001b[0m              \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mEffective (runtime)\u001b[0m                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m───────────────┼───────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────\u001b[0m                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K"]
[98.125849, "o", "\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mdefault-agent\u001b[0m \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m_not set_ (\u001b[36m:agent\u001b[0m section is \u001b[36mnil\u001b[0m)\u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mfalls back to built-in default                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mmax-iterations\u001b[0m\u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m_not set_                        \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97m100\u001b[0m                                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mNotes\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • The project's \u001b[36mconfig.edn\u001b[0m has \u001b[1;97mno explicit \u001b[36m:agent\u001b[0m section\u001b[0m — both keys are unset at project scope, so \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m     they inherit runtime/schema defaults.                                                              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[36m:max-iterations\u001b[0m resolves to"]
[98.125869, "o", " \u001b[1;97m100\u001b[0m at runtime.                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[36m:default-agent\u001b[0m has no persisted project value; the runtime uses its built-in default.              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • No secrets, API keys, or tokens were read or shown.                                                \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[32m│ \u001b[0mIf you want to pin either value for this repo, I can write \u001b[36m[:agent :default-agent]\u001b[0m and/or \u001b[36m[:agent\u001b[0m    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[25;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[32m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[36m:max-iterations]\u001b[0m to project scope — just say the word and I'll preview the diff first.               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[26;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m└───────────────────────────────────────────────"]
