[98.139655, "o", "\u001b[1;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mSHOW intent — pure read. I already read the :agent section at :project scope in iteration 1. The \u001b[0m\u001b[2;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mpersisted project config shows {:agent nil} — no explicit :agent section is set in the project's \u001b[0m\u001b[3;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mconfig.edn. The runtime effective value for :max-iterations is 100. :default-agent is not persisted \u001b[0m\u001b[4;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mat project scope (nil). No secrets involved. I have enough to answer without re-reading.\u001b[0m\u001b[5;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[6;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\u001b[0m\u001b[7;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mProject Config — Agent Settings\u001b[0m                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m  "]
