[110.630841, "o", "\u001b[1;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mSetting\u001b[0m       \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mPersisted (project)\u001b[0m              \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mEffective (runtime)\u001b[0m                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[2;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m───────────────┼───────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────\u001b[0m                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[3;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mdefault-agent\u001b[0m \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m_not set_ (\u001b[36m:agent\u001b[0m section is \u001b[36mnil\u001b[0m)\u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mfalls back to built-in default                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[4;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mmax-iterations\u001b[0m\u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m_not set_                        \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97m100\u001b[0m                                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[5;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[6;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m"]
[110.630851, "o", "│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mNotes\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[7;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • The project's \u001b[36mconfig.edn\u001b[0m has \u001b[1;97mno explicit \u001b[36m:agent\u001b[0m section\u001b[0m — both keys are unset at project scope, so \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m     they inherit runtime/schema defaults.                                                              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[36m:max-iterations\u001b[0m resolves to \u001b[1;97m100\u001b[0m at runtime.                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[36m:default-agent\u001b[0m has no persisted project value; the runtime uses its built-in default.              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • No secrets, API keys, or tokens were read or shown.                                                \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[12;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                        \u001b[92"]
[110.630866, "o", "m│\u001b[0m\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[32m│ \u001b[0mIf you want to pin either value for this repo, I can write \u001b[36m[:agent :default-agent]\u001b[0m and/or \u001b[36m[:agent\u001b[0m    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[32m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[36m:max-iterations]\u001b[0m to project scope — just say the word and I'll preview the diff first.               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K                                                                           \u001b[2m7 calls │ 239,438 tokens │ $0.4525\u001b[0m\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[1m\u001b[96m\u001b[100m❯ Set this project's default agent to plan-agent and max-iterations to 40. Target PROJECT scope only — do NOT\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K  touch user scope. Show me the diff "]
[110.630891, "o", "for just those two keys, then snapshot and persist the change. Proceed\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K  and persist without waiting for further confirmation. Don't print any secrets.\u001b[0m\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;96m+\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(33050 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(12.5s)\u001b[0m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mTUNE intent: set [:agent :default-agent] :plan-agent and [:agent :max-iterations] 40 at PROJECT \u001b[0m\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mscope. Both keys are in the allowlist and not security-sensitive. User explicitly authorized \u001b[0m\u001b[25;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mproceeding without further confirmation. I already have the project read from turn 1. I'll first run \u001b[0m\u001b[26;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mconfig$apply :confirm? false to capture the exact diff (the required preview step), then in the next \u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2miteration apply with :confirm? true. These are dependent (need to see diff first), so just the \u001b[0m\u001b[28;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mpreview call now.\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;93m⠏\u001b[0m\u001b[2m]\u001b[0m \u001b[96mMulling...\u001b[0m\u001b[2m (12."]
