[125.882213, "o", "\u001b[1;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[36m:default-agent\u001b[0m has no persisted project value; the runtime uses its built-in default.              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[2;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • No secrets, API keys, or tokens were read or shown.                                                \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[3;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[4;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[32m│ \u001b[0mIf you want to pin either value for this repo, I can write \u001b[36m[:agent :default-agent]\u001b[0m and/or \u001b[36m[:agent\u001b[0m    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[5;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[32m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[36m:max-iterations]\u001b[0m to project scope — just say the word and I'll preview the diff first.               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[6;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────"]
[125.882227, "o", "───────────────────────┘\u001b[0m\u001b[7;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K                                                                           \u001b[2m7 calls │ 239,438 tokens │ $0.4525\u001b[0m\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[1m\u001b[96m\u001b[100m❯ Set this project's default agent to plan-agent and max-iterations to 40. Target PROJECT scope only — do NOT\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K  touch user scope. Show me the diff for just those two keys, then snapshot and persist the change. Proceed\u001b[12;1H\u001b[2K  and persist without waiting for further confirmation. Don't print any secrets.\u001b[0m\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(33050 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(12.5s)\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mTUNE intent: set [:agent :default-agent] :plan-agent and [:agent :max-iterations] 40 at PROJECT \u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mscope. Both keys are in the allowlist and not security-sensitive. User explicitly authorized \u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mproceeding without further confirmation. I already have the p"]
[125.882247, "o", "roject read from turn 1. I'll first run \u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mconfig$apply :confirm? false to capture the exact diff (the required preview step), then in the next \u001b[0m\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2miteration apply with :confirm? true. These are dependent (need to see diff first), so just the \u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mpreview call now.\u001b[0m\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mconfig$apply\u001b[0m({\"proposed\" \"{\\\"agent\\\":{\\\"default-agent\\\":\\\"plan-agent\\\"...): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 2ms, 34 chars\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;96m+\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 2 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(33781 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(15.2s)\u001b[0m\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mThe JSON tool-call passed `proposed` as a string, which config$apply rejected (\":proposed must be a \u001b[0m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mmap\"). The fix is to call it from a clojure fence where I can pass an actual map literal. TUNE \u001b[0m\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mintent: set [:agent :default-agent] :plan-agent and [:agent :max-iterations] 40 at PROJECT scope — \u001b[0m\u001b[25;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mbot"]
[125.882279, "o", "h allowlisted, not security-sensitive. User authorized proceeding without further confirmation. \u001b[0m\u001b[26;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mI'll run the required diff preview (confirm? false) to capture the unified diff, then immediately \u001b[0m\u001b[27;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mapply (confirm? true) since the user explicitly said proceed/persist. Both in one sequential clojure \u001b[0m\u001b[28;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mblock.\u001b[0m\u001b[29;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;93m⠦\u001b[0m\u001b[2m]\u001b[0m \u001b[96mDeliberating...\u001b[0m\u001b[2m (27.6s)\u001b[0m"]
