[187.917226, "o", "✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(31576 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(7.0s)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mSHOW intent — pure read, no write. User wants project-scope :default-agent and :max-iterations. I'll \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mread the :agent section at :project scope. No secrets involved in these keys.\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mconfig$read\u001b[0m({\"section\" :agent, \"scope\" :project}): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 2ms, 5.2k chars\r\n\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 2 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(39.4s)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 3 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(34879 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(40.0s)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mSHOW intent — pure read. I already read the :agent section at :project scope in iteration 1. The \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mpersisted project config shows {:agent nil} — no explicit :agent section is set in the project's \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mconfig.edn. The runtime effective value for :max-iterations is 100. :default-agent is not persisted \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mat project scope (nil). No secrets"]
[187.917256, "o", " involved. I have enough to answer without re-reading.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[92m┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mProject Config — Agent Settings\u001b[0m                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m Read from project scope: \u001b[36m<repo>/.brainyard/config.edn\u001b[0m                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mSetting\u001b[0m       \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mPersisted (project)\u001b[0m          "]
[187.917289, "o", "    \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mEffective (runtime)\u001b[0m                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m───────────────┼───────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────\u001b[0m                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mdefault-agent\u001b[0m \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m_not set_ (\u001b[36m:agent\u001b[0m section is \u001b[36mnil\u001b[0m)\u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mfalls back to built-in default                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mmax-iterations\u001b[0m\u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m_not set_                        \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97m100\u001b[0m                                               \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mNotes\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m"]
